parameters: "Another subject has been entirely drained. If we don't do something about it the Lady's situation is going to become unsustainable."
"It is necessary to arrange another shipment of vessels before the next Mana Surge."
\n<Wounded Soldier>How...\.\.\. *cough*\.\. ...\.\.\. how did you get here?
\n<Wounded Soldier>It doesn't matter...\.\.\. you have to...\.\.\. get out...\.\.\.
\n<Wounded Soldier>Something's off with everyone coming back from that hellish Hole...\.\.\. \c[18]that maid\c[0] too...\.\.\.
\n<Wounded Soldier>You too...\.\.\. huhu...\.\.\. *cough*\.\. something similiar has happened to you too?\.\.
\n<Wounded Soldier>Then maybe you can...\.\.\. *cough*...\.\.\. get to the truth...\.\.\. I tried to warn my superiors...\.\.\. but it was too late...\.\.\. Captain Aaron...\.\.\.
\n<Wounded Soldier>Take this \c[18]\ii[8]\c[0]...\.\.\. I won't last much longer...\.\.\. my blood...\.\.\.
\n<Wounded Soldier>...\.\.\. I won't last much longer...\.\.\. go now...\.\.\. that maid surely...\.\.\. *cough*\.\. will notice soon about our little chat...\.\.\.
\n<Wounded Soldier>...\.\.\. I'm sorry for dragging you into this...\.\.\. Captian Aaron...\.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>Just got done fixing up all the beds in the quarters,\. but my work for the day isn't finished until I've made sure all the sickles are polished and grinded.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>Our weapons have to be maintained to the highest lethal standard possible,\. if we're to protect our Lady in her time of ailing health.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>I will not rest until my duties are complete,\. for her sake.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>The head maid was kind enough to go through the effort of capturing and bringing this criminal here.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>I have to watch over him to make sure he doesn't escape,\. our Lady needs his blood for her treatment.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>I'll stay here until Miss Kanako returns to harvest,\. hopefully this batch will prove better than the ones before.\.\.
\n<\N[1]>Got you,\. servant!\.\. You can't run away now!
\n<\N[1]>What did you do to blondie?\.\.\. \BST[1,Neneko2]Actually,\. that's not even important right now...
\n<\N[1]>You were on my case since the beginning!\.\. I finally get to mess you up,\. \C[18]servant\C[0]!
\n<Headmaid Kanako>What an unruly kitten,\. you are.\.\. Let me show you what happens to anyone who misbehaves in my Mansion...
